  "body": "### Description\r\n\r\nIt would be nice if `quarkus-mailer` could introduce an extension point so extensions could integrate with some major e-mail campaign providers out there (eg. Amazon Simple Email Service, Postmark, Mailjet, and SendGrid).\r\n\r\n\r\n### Implementation ideas\r\n\r\nIt would be interesting if other extensions could provide a `Mailer`/`ReactiveMailer` implementation (through some new Build items perhaps or by introducing an SPI in `quarkus-mailer` ?).\r\n\r\nThis would allow the `ses` extension in https://github.com/quarkiverse/quarkus-amazon-services/tree/main/ses to provide a `SeSMailer` implementation, for example.",
